{
    "analysis": "From the provided file summaries we confirmed metric.csv contains the candidate root-cause component types (db_001–db_013, docker_001–docker_008, os_001–os_022) and that trace.csv covers docker and two OS nodes. We have not yet computed global thresholds (required to detect anomalies) nor have we filtered metrics to the incident window (May 23, 2020 01:00–01:30, UTC+8). Next we must calculate global thresholds (P95/P90/P50/P5) for each component-KPI time series using the full available series (no time filtering yet) and retain the aggregated table in kernel for later filtering and anomaly detection. No anomaly detection or trace analysis has been performed yet.",
